Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones who shrunk my body, the Black Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With each move I've made toward grasping the Organization's weakness thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI has been a figure that supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Gin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Akai Suuichi\NFBI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The covert plan underlying our strategy to bring an end to the Organization remains undiscovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Vermouth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena / Hondou Hidemi\NCIA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the condition that her brother Eisuke was admitted to the Witness Protection program...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena agreed to return to the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several days later, when we went to a hotel buffet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got involved in the murder case of the president of Foreign Talent Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whereupon one of the suspects turned out to be the FBI agent Camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,James Black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Jodie Starling\NFBI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jodie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running in the darkness â€” a red scream and a black shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Undercover in the Organization, Mizunashi Rena is given the command to rub out Akai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:03:01.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NINNOCENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This evil looking man is with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:17.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Andre Camel (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when they're considering agents for the Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They don't judge them by their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is he here in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that I messed up a job for the FBI and came to Japan to console myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I took so long to come back, he got worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, Andre Camel is my lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so? Why are you still in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think her Japanese is getting a bit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before, she was saying things like, "sou desssu."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's because I've been taking a crash course from Andre, who's really good at Japanese, that I've improved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And both of us have just found it difficult to leave Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's exactly right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, that seems a bit contrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, even if he is with the FBI, that doesn't exclude him as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need you to stay until you're cleared of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the FBI pulls out of the hospital, I want to see you all once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this paper bag in the tool storage area in the rooftop restaurant plaza restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside was a raincoat, gloves, and a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These may have been used by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we probably won't find any gunpowder when we examine these three suspects clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, if they had disposed of the clothes they used for the crime, the culprit could have forced their way into the crowded elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit took the stairs to the roof and went into the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then put their gloves, clothing, and gun in a paper bag and hid it in the tool storage area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means at least five minutes would have passed before they were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have looked suspicious if they did all of that in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They also probably wouldn't have expected the police to arrive this quickly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we also checked the video from the security cameras in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no foreigners on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Asian foreigners?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know from their appearance, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:02.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Irina Palmer (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do not think the president employed any Asian people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president always said:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A person who doesn't look Japanese at all and yet speaks Japanese is interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the suspicious ones are still those three people there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the most suspicious person...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the one who was hiding in the restroom, Hal{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:25.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hal Buckner (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already said I wasn't hiding, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you normally avoid hiding in the same restroom where you hid that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say the investigators and officers coming, you could have gone back in there to hide without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, the coat is fitted for slender men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The length would exactly match Toby{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Toby Keynes (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With something that size, this FBI guy could force himself into it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, it's not just us three men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secretary could have worn it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As they say, "better too big than too small."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She could have been lying up to now in order to deceive us over her own crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need to consider that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have worn a man's coat to make it seem like a man was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, it seems certain that one of you four were responsible for making the president eat those bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, other than the bullets, the president really was eating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the president's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look like he was holding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it does seem that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no food on top of the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like he was eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like he was holding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That pen on the desk or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only a small amount, but there are traces of blood on the shaft of the pen and on the memo paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are also slight traces of writing on the memo paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the president have written something before he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the culprit took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, have a blood analysis performed and determine what was written.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, confirm it was the president's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how we would investigate it, right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the blood on the memo paper belonged to President Sunouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and they say the writing on the memo was his as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? What was on the memo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written in English so I'm not sure what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even if it's a dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring my tux.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring my tux?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watashi no tuxedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...tottekiitte kure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Continuing with this job is becoming mentally stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If possible, I want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the human resources manager at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them clearly that I couldn't be an announcer any longer and needed to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's troublesome to have them ineptly searching for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Organization can hear every word I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are all sorts of bugs and transmitters on me right now and always two or three guards watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That person{\i0} that even now continues to suspect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a mission for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to relay an order from {\i1}that person{\i0} that suspects so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will eliminate someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To prove you can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eliminate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI agent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI agent, Akai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been mulling over how suspicious it was, {\i1}that person{\i0} and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How extremely easy it was to recover you from the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the plan is to have you kill the FBI's trump card, Akai Shuuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have you prove your innocence to us personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've got some reason preventing you from doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin, how can I approach Akai when even you don't know how to handle him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I approach them poorly, they'll capture me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't approach him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will only lure him into our firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You returned to the Organization just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are now being treated like a black sheep due to your mistake and capture at the hands of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you no longer have a place here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to leave us and flee to a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say all that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you will deal only with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you offer some sort of rewarding information, he'll definitely bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when he comes in blindly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all will come forward and shoot him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll handle that on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His nose is surprisingly sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he detects our presence, he'll see through the trap and turn his heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be letting us observe the course of events from a location where his bullets cannot reach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll place a bug on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And of course, a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you've asked, but can you give me a little time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll call him now, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you fail to, you'll be calling the Grim Reaper instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure the FBI will want to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a possibility, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the intel from our guy, they're still holding up in that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, one of their agents has somehow become involved in a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI's eyes are all focused on him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot miss this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some company president found himself with extra airholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just your usual murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring my tuxedo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what was written on the memo the president left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring my tux."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring" is "to get"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And "tux" is short for "tuxedo".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pen and paper both have the president's blood on them, and it's in his handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, there's the memo paper that was torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stricken president wrote it as he was dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the culprit noticed it and took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be a "daiingu messeeji"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you are English teachers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's true that I teach English at a cram school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't these people FBI agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For various reasons, I was teaching for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, secretary Irina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know what he meant by "bring my tuxedo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was a message from the president to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was going to a party tonight, so he asked me to bring his tuxedo by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's just a regular memo that has nothing to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president said he was going out this afternoon for a meal with an up and coming talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was for when I returned while he was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're the one who tore out the memo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I saw the president was dead, I called right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did not touch anything until the policemen came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I did know about the tuxedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left a message about it on the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answering machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you already out, President sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the file you asked for and am bringing it there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll get the tuxedo for the party tonight later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friday, 1:27 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the culprit heard this and hurried away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the culprit recorded it after the crime to make us think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's at least possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If "Bring my tux" has some sort of hidden meaning in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have purposely mentioned the tuxedo in the message in order to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you mention a tuxedo, the one who that points to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be this man, who was working as a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the work we models usually do, wearing all sorts of clothes stylishly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just tuxedos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president was going to wear one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, in any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be investigating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone please go wait in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi, you figured out something about the memo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president could have added something to a previous memo to make it a dying message, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, forensics should have noticed the additional writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything to add or remove from these English letters to change the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, I'm not sure this is the best time to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said just the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you came to Japan two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu was still undercover in the Organization then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you must have heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About our failure to capture an executive member of theirs due to an agent's mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The agent who made that mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had arranged to meet that executive in a warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were all lying in wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lone old man appeared and sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was ignoring him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for me, without thinking, I yelled:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You should get out of here, it's dangerous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:19:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the old man you drove away was one of their members checking on the arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to that, the executive never showed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they discovered that Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some undercover investigation had failed and there was an agent who returned to the office with his head held in shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked if anyone was up for the plan this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can handle the driving job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'll come to Japan right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He warned me that I could die, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mistake was the cause of his girlfriend's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me not to worry about it, that his girlfriend had been aware of the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be putting an end to it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to fool me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of something better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be surprised at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you knew, why didn't you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew I was just using you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you not tell without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your phone has been ringing for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it OK to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're surprised, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I contacted you so soon after returning to the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's become difficult to stay in the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want your help to leave and fly out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll offer any information that the FBI wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we meet now, just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll mail you the time and place after this call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is Friday the 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have believed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That his fate would be sealed on such an appropriate day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Mizunashi Rena on the phone, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked if we could meet now in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A private meeting with her could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be more prudent not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, except...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it is a trap and I do not show, in 7 or 8 cases out of 9, she'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confident my sixth sense will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may just be CIA...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I believe she has a clever plan to get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-At any rate, I'll call Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} so we FBI can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The message left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The summoning call.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do they imply a trap or a cry for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we take a risk by going on the offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we jump in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A glimpse of the unexpected truth hidden behind their evil ways is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Detective Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:29.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NREADY TO DIE
